THAT I WOULD RECOVER
FASTER IF I DID,

15:01.460 --> 15:02.996
AND I'M TRYING.

15:03.000 --> 15:04.797
THAT'S NOT THE REASON

15:04.800 --> 15:06.791
WE'RE NOT GOING
TO DO YOUR SURGERIES.

15:06.800 --> 15:08.358
THEN WHY
AREN'T YOU THEN?

15:08.370 --> 15:10.133
YOU SAID YOU COULD
MAKE ME LOOK BETTER!

15:10.140 --> 15:11.437
I NEED TO LOOK BETTER!

15:11.440 --> 15:15.103
MS. BABCOCK, WE'RE
DECLINING YOUR CASE

15:15.110 --> 15:19.240
BECAUSE WE FEEL LIKE YOU HAVE
UNREALISTIC EXPECTATIONS.

15:19.250 --> 15:21.115
BUT EVERY DOCTOR HAS
THEIR OWN CRITERIA.

15:21.120 --> 15:24.044
I'D LIKE TO RECOMMEND MY
COLLEAGUE DR. MARTIN HARGROVE.

15:24.050 --> 15:26.211
I DON'T HAVE TIME TO DO
A CONSULTATION

15:26.220 --> 15:28.188
AND THE SCHEDULING
ALL OVER AGAIN!

15:28.190 --> 15:30.556
I NEED TO
LOOK DIFFERENT NOW!

15:30.560 --> 15:32.425
YOU STOP PLAYING
MIND GAMES WITH ME.

15:32.430 --> 15:34.921
IF YOU WANT ME TO PAY
MORE MONEY, I'LL PAY IT.

15:34.930 --> 15:37.797
IT'S NOT ABOUT MONEY,
MS. BABCOCK, IT'S--

15:37.800 --> 15:39.995
I HOPE YOU GET CANCER!

15:40.000 --> 15:41.331
[SLAMS TELEPHONE
ON THE FLOOR]

16:22.880 --> 16:24.370
* I'LL SELL MY SOUL *

16:24.380 --> 16:26.439
* I'LL BE YOUR GEEK *

16:26.450 --> 16:29.613
* I'LL RUN OUT IN... *

16:29.620 --> 16:31.508
DID IT HURT?

16:32.790 --> 16:35.554
YOU WERE WORTH IT.

16:40.800 --> 16:43.166
THE STITCHES COME OUT
NEXT WEEK.

16:43.170 --> 16:46.298
WE CAN DO IT ANYTIME
AFTER THAT.

16:49.540 --> 16:52.759
MATT, HAVE YOU URINATED
YET TODAY?

16:52.770 --> 16:54.635
[LAUGHS]

16:54.640 --> 16:56.130
BUZZKILL.

16:57.780 --> 16:59.304
LATER.

17:03.550 --> 17:05.017
BYE.

17:07.190 --> 17:08.259
WHY DO YOU WANT TO SEE THIS?

17:08.260 --> 17:09.682
I HAD TO SUTURE
YOUR URINARIUS,

17:09.690 --> 17:11.920
AND I WANT TO MAKE SURE THERE'S
NO BLOOD IN THE URINE.

17:11.930 --> 17:14.649
THAT IT COULD BE A SIGN
OF INTERNAL HEMORRHAGING...

17:14.660 --> 17:18.096
AND I WANT TO BE HERE
TO SUPPORT YOU.

17:18.100 --> 17:20.091
WHY DO I NEED THAT?

17:20.100 --> 17:22.261
THE FIRST TIME YOU PEE
AFTER AN OPERATION

17:22.270 --> 17:23.828
OF THIS NATURE,
IT'S GOING TO FEEL LIKE

17:23.840 --> 17:25.398
YOU'RE PISSING FIRE, MATT.

17:25.410 --> 17:29.073
JUST PRESS DOWN ON MY HAND
AND SCREAM IF YOU WANT.

17:29.080 --> 17:31.401
NOBODY'S GONNA JUDGE YOU.

17:33.450 --> 17:37.739
I--I DON'T NEED
TO HOLD YOUR HAND, DAD.

17:37.750 --> 17:39.388
AND, UH...

17:39.390 --> 17:42.052
COULD YOU GIVE ME
SOME PRIVACY?

17:42.060 --> 17:43.789
OH.

17:54.600 --> 17:58.138
VANESSA'S A LITTLE
HARDBODY, MATT.

17:58.140 --> 18:00.279
LOOKS LIKE YOU'RE DATING
A FUTURE PROM QUEEN.

18:00.280 --> 18:02.771
CONGRATULATIONS.

18:09.820 --> 18:11.685
I CAN'T DANCE.

18:11.690 --> 18:14.488
OK, WELL, LET'S COME BACK
IN AN HOUR THEN.

18:14.490 --> 18:16.458
NO, I, UH...

18:16.460 --> 18:17.950
I MEAN I REALLY
CAN'T DANCE.

18:17.960 --> 18:19.222
YOU'RE RIGHT ABOUT
THE PROM THING.

18:19.230 --> 18:21.698
SHE'S ALREADY
ASKED ME TO GO...

18:21.700 --> 18:25.090
AND I DON'T--I DON'T
KNOW HOW TO DANCE.

18:25.100 --> 18:28.137
UH...

18:28.140 --> 18:30.233
WELL, THAT'S OK.

18:30.240 --> 18:32.504
NEITHER COULD I.

18:32.510 --> 18:36.139
YOU JUST SAY,
"IT'S NOT MY THING."

18:38.080 --> 18:39.377
THIS WORKS?

18:39.380 --> 18:41.917
I DIDN'T EVEN HAVE TO DANCE
AT MY OWN WEDDING.

18:41.920 --> 18:45.378
WOMEN LIKE IT WHEN THERE'S
SOME MYSTERY THERE.

18:53.930 --> 18:55.522
THAN KS.

18:55.530 --> 18:57.418
YEAH.

18:59.730 --> 19:01.664
OH, SHIT, IT'S COMING!

19:01.670 --> 19:03.934
UH, HAND.

19:03.940 --> 19:05.362
YO HO HO. HA!

19:05.370 --> 19:06.632
[SPEAKING SPANISH]

19:11.210 --> 19:12.677
[BOTH CONVERSE IN SPANISH]

19:34.000 --> 19:35.297
HELLO?

19:35.300 --> 19:36.528
WHERE ARE YOU?

19:36.540 --> 19:38.462
WE HAVE A HIS-AND-HER LIPO
IN HALF AN HOUR.

19:38.470 --> 19:40.006
CAR TROUBLE.
I'LL BE THERE.

19:40.010 --> 19:41.534
SINCE I'VE GOT YOU,

19:41.540 --> 19:44.008
WHY DID YOU SCHEDULE ANOTHER
NECK LIFT FOR MRS. GRUBMAN?

19:44.010 --> 19:46.171
I DIDN'T SCHEDULE
THAT OPERATION.

19:46.180 --> 19:48.045
WELL, WHO DID THEN,
THE FILOFAX FAIRY?

19:48.050 --> 19:50.109
I'M SITTING HERE REVIEWING
NEXT MONTH'S SURGERIES,

19:50.120 --> 19:52.111
AND HERE IT IS IN PEN
ON THE 15th.

19:52.120 --> 19:53.280
I'M TELLING YOU, SEAN,

19:53.290 --> 19:54.484
I DIDN'T SCHEDULE
THAT OPERATION.

19:54.490 --> 19:56.287
I SLICED THAT
BITCH'S WADDLE OFF

19:56.290 --> 19:57.484
15 MONTHS AGO.

19:57.490 --> 19:59.082
THAT'S WHAT I THOUGHT.

19:59.090 --> 20:02.093
CALL MRS. GRUBMAN AND TELL HER
YOU MADE A SCHEDULING MISTAKE.

20:02.100 --> 20:04.193
I'LL SEE YOU IN A FEW.

20:07.440 --> 20:09.328
[CELL PHONE RINGS]

20:10.570 --> 20:13.368
DR. TROY,
WHAT A NICE SURPRISE.

20:13.380 --> 20:15.701
I'M HEALING BEAUTIFULLY.

20:15.710 --> 20:18.099
WHAT A DOLL YOU ARE
TO CHECK UP ON ME.

20:18.110 --> 20:19.839
LISTEN, SINCE I'VE
GOT YOU ON THE HORN,

20:19.850 --> 20:22.444
HOW MANY AMBIENS SHOULD
I TAKE IF I WANT TO

20:22.450 --> 20:24.441
SLEEP THROUGH
THE ENTIRE 8-HOUR FLIGHT

20:24.450 --> 20:26.611
AND WAKE UP REFRESHED
IN TAHITI?

20:26.620 --> 20:28.986
MRS. GRUBMAN, WHO SIGNED
YOU UP FOR ANOTHER NECK LIFT?

20:28.990 --> 20:30.059
I DID IT MYSELF

20:30.060 --> 20:31.379
WITH THE GIRL
AT THE FRONT DESK.

20:31.390 --> 20:32.652
YOU WERE WITH A PATIENT,

20:32.660 --> 20:35.458
AND YOU MADE IT CLEAR
I'M NOT TO INTERRUPT.

20:35.460 --> 20:37.269
I DIDN'T APPROVE
THAT OPERATION.

20:37.270 --> 20:39.067
LOOK,
I'M CO-HOSTING A BENEFIT

20:39.070 --> 20:40.196
WITH BLAINE TRUMP
NEXT MONTH,

20:40.200 --> 20:41.929
AND I NEED
TO LOOK MY BEST.

20:41.940 --> 20:44.329
NEVER SCHEDULE ANOTHER
OPERATION WITHOUT MY CONSENT!

20:44.340 --> 20:45.432
AM I CLEAR?

20:45.440 --> 20:48.671
I DON'T LIKE YOUR TONE,
DR. TROY,

20:48.680 --> 20:50.375
AND THE NEXT TIME YOU
SPEAK TO ME THAT WAY,

20:50.380 --> 20:52.598
TAKE A MINUTE TO REMEMBER
WHO'S KEEPING YOU

20:52.610 --> 20:54.669
IN THOSE GUCCI SUITS
YOU LOVE SO MUCH.

20:54.680 --> 20:55.669
[BEEP]

20:55.680 --> 20:57.238
MA'AM, I NEED YOU
TO CLEAR YOUR POCKETS

20:57.250 --> 20:58.547
AND GO THROUGH AGAIN.

20:58.550 --> 21:00.381
LOOSEN YOUR BRAIDS AND
TAKE A LOOK, SWEETHEART.

21:00.390 --> 21:01.914
DO I LOOK
LIKE A TERRORIST?

21:01.920 --> 21:04.889
MA'AM, I NEED YOU
TO GO THROUGH AGAIN.

21:04.890 --> 21:07.654
PUT YOUR PHONE IN
THE CLEARANCE BASKET...

21:07.660 --> 21:08.797
PLEASE.

21:08.800 --> 21:10.461
MRS. GRUBMAN?

21:10.470 --> 21:12.290
HOLD ON, DR. TROY.

21:16.840 --> 21:18.705
[BEEP]

21:18.710 --> 21:19.631
[BEEP]

21:19.640 --> 21:20.504
MA'AM.

21:20.510 --> 21:22.102
I AM KEEPING
THE MAINTENANCE

21:22.110 --> 21:23.475
AS SCHEDULED,
DR. TROY.

21:23.480 --> 21:24.708
NO, YOU'RE NOT!

21:24.710 --> 21:26.541
IT GOES AGAINST
A.S.A.P.S. GUIDELINES.

21:26.550 --> 21:28.370
IT'S NOT ETHICAL.

21:28.380 --> 21:29.449
PLEASE, DR.TROY.
SINCE WHEN

21:29.450 --> 21:30.883
HAVE YOU
EVER BEEN ETHICAL?

21:30.890 --> 21:32.778
MRS. GRUBMAN, THAT'S IT.
I'M CUTTING YOU OFF.

21:32.790 --> 21:35.759
MY OFFICE WILL NO LONGER
SCHEDULE SURGERIES WITH YOU.

21:35.760 --> 21:37.421
[HANGS UP PHONE]

21:37.430 --> 21:39.227
DR. TROY!

21:39.230 --> 21:40.424
UH...HELLO?

21:40.430 --> 21:41.658
MA'AM, I NEED--

21:41.660 --> 21:43.560
LOOK, YOUR MACHINE
IS BROKE!

21:43.570 --> 21:45.458
I AM NOT MISSING
THAT FLIGHT.

21:45.470 --> 21:48.860
WE'VE GOT A RUNNER.

21:51.340 --> 21:53.604
[DON'T BRING ME DOWNPLAYING]

22:00.080 --> 22:01.513
OH!

22:01.520 --> 22:03.943
AND AS YOU CAN SEE,
HERE IS THE CAUTERY TIP

22:03.950 --> 22:06.942
YOU LEFT INSIDE MY CLIENT'S
STOMACH AFTER HER TUMMY TUCK.

22:06.950 --> 22:09.418
WITHOUT DOUBT,
THIS IS THE METAL OBJECT

22:09.420 --> 22:10.819
THAT SET OFF THE AIRPORT
SECURITY SYSTEM

22:10.830 --> 22:13.390
AND LED TO THE ASSAULT
OF MY CLIENT.

22:13.400 --> 22:16.028
SHE HAD THE OBJECT
QUIETLY REMOVED

22:16.030 --> 22:17.566
BY HER PRIVATE PHYSICIAN

22:17.570 --> 22:22.564
AT CONSIDERABLE PAIN
AND EXPENSE.

22:22.570 --> 22:26.904
MRS. GRUBMAN, LET ME BEGIN
BY SAYING HOW TRULY SORRY--

22:26.910 --> 22:27.899
DR. MCNAMARA,

22:27.910 --> 22:30.470
SEEING AS THIS INCIDENT,
TOP TO BOTTOM,

22:30.480 --> 22:32.573
WAS CAUSED
BY YOUR PARTNER,

22:32.580 --> 22:36.619
I THINK IT IS HE
WHO SHOULD APOLOGIZE.

22:43.120 --> 22:47.079
MR. AMBROSE, WHAT KIND OF
REPARATIONS ARE YOU LOOKING FOR?

22:47.090 --> 22:48.455
$10 MILLION...

22:48.460 --> 22:50.928
NOT A PENNY LESS.

22:50.930 --> 22:52.466
GODDAMN IT!

22:52.470 --> 22:54.563
YOU SHOULD HAVE DONE
AN INSTRUMENT COUNT, LIZ!

22:54.570 --> 22:57.038
I DID. THIS HAS NEVER
HAPPENED TO ME BEFORE.

22:57.040 --> 22:58.439
I AM ALWAYS SO CAREFUL.

22:58.440 --> 23:00.237
APPARENTLY,
NOT CAREFUL ENOUGH!

23:00.240 --> 23:01.832
WE COULD LOSE THE BUSINESS
OVER THIS!

23:01.840 --> 23:04.308
I CANNOT BELIEVE
YOUR INEPTITUDE!

23:04.310 --> 23:05.299
SEAN--

23:05.310 --> 23:06.299
HOLD ON, CHRISTIAN.

23:06.310 --> 23:08.244
THIS IS BETWEEN ME
AND HIM.

23:08.250 --> 23:09.842
YOU EXAMINED
GRUBMAN'S BELLY

23:09.850 --> 23:11.340
AFTER I DID
AN INSTRUMENT CHECK,

23:11.350 --> 23:13.887
CORRECT, SEAN?
I MEAN, THAT'S PROTOCOL.

23:16.760 --> 23:18.250
WAIT.

23:18.260 --> 23:20.251
ARE WE TO BELIEVE
FROM YOUR SILENCE

23:20.260 --> 23:21.591
THAT MAYBE
YOU DIDN'T DO IT

23:21.600 --> 23:23.465
BECAUSE YOU
WERE TOO DISTRACT ED

23:23.470 --> 23:26.064
WITH YOUR
SON'S CIRCUMCISION?

23:26.070 --> 23:28.561
WHAT INEPTITUDE!

23:28.570 --> 23:32.108
LIZ, LOOK...I'M UPSET.

23:32.110 --> 23:33.361
SCREW IT!

23:33.370 --> 23:36.407
I SHOULD NEVER
HAVE COME BACK HERE!

23:36.410 --> 23:37.547
I AM RESIGNING!

23:37.550 --> 23:38.778
NO, YOU'RE NOT.

23:38.780 --> 23:41.578
LIZ, PLEASE,
CAN YOU GIVE US A MINUTE?

23:45.390 --> 23:47.415
OHH.

23:50.060 --> 23:52.824
I CAN'T BELIEVE THIS.

23:54.600 --> 23:56.750
IRONIC, ISN'T IT,
THAT AFTER YEARS

23:56.760 --> 24:00.321
OF MY ENDURING YOUR
"BE MORE RESPONSIBLE" LECTURES,

24:00.330 --> 24:02.935
YOU'RE THE ONE WHO SCREWED US?

24:06.470 --> 24:09.530
LOOK, WE HAVE
MALPRACT ICE INSURANCE

24:09.540 --> 24:11.576
PRECISELY FOR THIS REASON.

24:11.580 --> 24:13.104
IF WE PAY OUT, WE
ARE SCREWED, CHRISTIAN.

24:13.110 --> 24:14.714
OUR RATES TRIPLE,
AND THEN, BASICALLY,

24:14.720 --> 24:16.574
WE'RE WORKING
TO BREAK EVEN.

24:16.580 --> 24:18.480
WHAT IF SHE
GOES TO THE MEDIA?

24:18.490 --> 24:20.708
OUR PROFESSIONAL LIVES
ARE OVER!

24:25.560 --> 24:27.494
YOU HAVE TO GO TO HER.

24:29.860 --> 24:31.293
ME?

24:31.300 --> 24:32.665
SHE LIKES YOU.
SHE TRUSTS YOU.

24:32.670 --> 24:34.035
IF YOU HADN'T CUT HER OFF,

24:34.040 --> 24:35.792
SHE PROBABLY WOULDN'T
HAVE BEEN SO VINDICT IVE.

24:35.800 --> 24:37.609
HEY, I CUT HER OFF
BECAUSE OF YOU.

24:37.610 --> 24:39.009
OH, I DIDN'T ASK YOU
TO DO THAT.

24:39.010 --> 24:40.307
NO? YOU'RE THE ONE

24:40.310 --> 24:41.379
WHO IS CONSTANTLY
BERATING ME

24:41.380 --> 24:43.473
ABOUT MY SUPPOSED LACK
OF ETHICS.

24:43.480 --> 24:45.107
YOU'RE THE REASON
I DUMPED GRUBMAN,

24:45.110 --> 24:46.577
AND YOU'RE THE REASON
NANETTE BABCOCK

24:46.580 --> 24:48.548
PULLED A GODDAMN
GLENN CLOSE ON MY CAR.

24:48.550 --> 24:49.915
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

24:49.920 --> 24:51.239
I WANTED TO HANDLE
THIS PATIENT DIFFERENTLY,

24:51.250 --> 24:53.684
MAKE HER IN SOME WAY
FEEL BETTER ABOUT HERSELF,

24:53.690 --> 24:55.681
BUT YOU AND YOUR
NEW PIECE-OF-ASS HIRE--

24:55.690 --> 24:57.453
I AM NOT INTERESTED
IN HER IN THAT WAY!

24:57.460 --> 24:58.449
WENT ALL DRACONIAN
ON ME,

24:58.460 --> 25:00.485
AND SHE TRASHED MY CAR!

25:02.200 --> 25:03.599
YOUR FINGERPRINTS

25:03.600 --> 25:05.864
ARE ALL OVER BOTH
CRIME SCENES, SEAN.

25:05.870 --> 25:09.431
HOW MANY WOMEN HAVE YOU
SCREWED OVER, CHRISTIAN?

25:09.440 --> 25:10.998
A HUNDRED? A THOUSAND?

25:11.010 --> 25:13.001
IT COULD EASILY BE ONE OF THEM.

25:15.080 --> 25:17.002
SHE DID IT, SEAN.

25:20.750 --> 25:22.411
YOU DEAL WITH GRUBMAN.

25:22.420 --> 25:25.082
I'LL INVESTIGATE
NANETTE BABCOCK...

25:25.090 --> 25:27.217
WITH GRACE.

25:30.360 --> 25:31.952
[POUNDING ON DOOR]

25:33.360 --> 25:34.691
HELLO?

25:42.500 --> 25:43.967
MS. BABCOCK?

26:19.670 --> 26:21.570
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

26:21.580 --> 26:23.002
UH, I'M SORRY.

26:23.010 --> 26:26.070
I KNOCKED ON THE DOOR,
AND IT OPENED.

26:26.080 --> 26:28.446
YOU DIDN'T ANSWER MY QUESTION.

26:28.450 --> 26:31.180
THE DOCTORS AND I
WERE WORRIED.

26:31.190 --> 26:33.715
I CAME BY TO SEE
HOW YOU WERE DOING.

26:33.720 --> 26:35.312
I'M DOING MY LAUNDRY.

26:35.320 --> 26:37.754
I'M MAKING MY LUNCH.

26:37.760 --> 26:40.695
I'M NOT GOING TO MY REUNION.

26:40.700 --> 26:42.759
THAT'S WHAT I'M DOING.

26:46.530 --> 26:48.395
NAN ETTE...

26:48.400 --> 26:51.198
YOU WENT OFF
YOUR LITHIUM.

26:51.210 --> 26:54.407
DOES YOUR TREATING PSYCHOLOGIST
KNOW ABOUT THAT?

26:54.410 --> 26:56.037
I QUIT SEEING HIM
A MONTH AGO.

26:56.040 --> 26:59.601
HE COULDN'T DO ANYTHING
TO MAKE ME FEEL BETTER.

26:59.610 --> 27:01.214
THAT'S WHY
I CAME TO YOU.

27:01.220 --> 27:03.848
YOU GUYS DID A SHITTY JOB
AT THAT, TOO.

27:03.850 --> 27:05.943
YOU SEE WHAT I'M EATING?

27:05.950 --> 27:09.989
BULLSHIT LOWFAT TURKEY
WITH NO BREAD.

27:09.990 --> 27:12.925
THE LITHIUM
MADE ME GAIN WEIGHT.

27:12.930 --> 27:15.592
I NEEDED TO BE THINNER
FOR MY REUNION.

27:15.600 --> 27:20.219
THAT'S WHY
I QUIT COLD TURKEY.

27:20.230 --> 27:24.360
JIM RECONIA WAS
GONNA BE AT MY REUNION.

27:26.740 --> 27:29.504
I BET HE WOULD
HAVE LOVED YOU,

27:29.510 --> 27:31.978
YOU WITH
YOUR PERFECT FACE

27:31.980 --> 27:35.143
AND YOUR TIGHT ASS
AND YOUR TITS

27:35.150 --> 27:37.687
THAT DON'T SAG DOWN
TO AN ELASTIC WAISTBAND

27:37.690 --> 27:40.318
THAT YOU DON'T
HAVE TO WEAR.

27:40.320 --> 27:44.256
I HATE GIRLS LIKE YOU.

27:44.260 --> 27:47.184
YOU ALWAYS GET THE JIMS
OF THIS WORLD.

27:47.190 --> 27:51.320
WAS JIM A FRIEND
OF YOURS, NANETTE?

27:51.330 --> 27:53.127
HE WAS THE CLASS PRESIDENT.

27:53.130 --> 27:56.634
I READ ON CLASSMATES DOT COM
THAT HE WAS RECENTLY DIVORCED.

27:56.640 --> 27:59.234
I THOUGHT, MAYBE
IF I LOOKED PRETTIER...

27:59.240 --> 28:01.435
LIKE ONE OF THEM...

28:01.440 --> 28:04.045
HE'D NOTICE ME...

28:04.050 --> 28:06.371
AND STRIKE UP A CONVERSATION.

28:06.380 --> 28:08.610
BUT YOU RUINED THAT.

28:08.620 --> 28:10.178
AND YOU RETALIATED

28:10.180 --> 28:12.978
BY VAN DALIZING
DR. TROY'S CAR?

28:12.990 --> 28:15.015
YOU THINK
I WOULD DO THAT?

28:15.020 --> 28:16.817
BECAUSE IF I'M UGLY,

28:16.820 --> 28:20.529
NATURALLY
I'M A CRAZY BITCH, TOO.

28:20.530 --> 28:22.521
IS THAT RIGHT?

28:22.530 --> 28:24.794
MS. BABCOCK,
NOTHING THAT HAPPENS

28:24.800 --> 28:27.360
IN A DOCTOR'S OFFICE
IS PERSONAL.

28:27.370 --> 28:30.464
YOU REJECTING ME AND
RUINING MY DREAM IS PERSONAL!

28:30.470 --> 28:33.928
YOU NOT MAKING ME THE BEST
I CAN BE IS PERSONAL!

28:33.940 --> 28:35.908
I GET REJECTED ALL THE TIME!

28:35.910 --> 28:39.209
BUT WHEN I OFFER TO PAY
AND STILL GET REJECT ED,

28:39.210 --> 28:41.849
THAT IS PERSONAL!

28:46.390 --> 28:47.880
PLEASE LEAVE.

28:59.870 --> 29:01.428
[SOFT MUSIC PLAYING]

29:01.440 --> 29:02.691
[FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING]

29:02.700 --> 29:05.100
SORRY TO KEEP YOU
WAITING, DR. TROY.

29:05.110 --> 29:07.533
I WAS HELD UP
ON THE PHONE.

29:07.540 --> 29:09.679
WELL, YOU KNOW
HOW HYSTERICAL

29:09.680 --> 29:10.806
YOUNG WOMEN CAN GET

29:10.810 --> 29:13.040
WHEN THEY FIND OUT
THEIR ONLY MOTHER

29:13.050 --> 29:15.473
ALMOST DIED ON
THE OPERATING TABLE.

29:15.480 --> 29:16.617
NOW, MRS. GRUBMAN,

29:16.620 --> 29:19.316
YOU DIDN'T ALMOST DIE
ON OUR TABLE.

29:19.320 --> 29:21.117
YOU DIDN'T EVEN SUFFER
FROM SEPSIS OR--

29:21.120 --> 29:23.259
OH, DROP THE TOUGH-LOVE
BULLSHIT.

29:23.260 --> 29:25.251
YOU DROVE ALL THE WAY
TO PALM BEACH

29:25.260 --> 29:26.784
FROM YOUR
MIAMI BUTCHER SHOP,

29:26.790 --> 29:30.294
AND I'M SURE IT WAS TO
GROVEL, NOT TO LECTURE.

29:32.400 --> 29:33.890
I'M SORRY.

29:33.900 --> 29:36.630
YEAH, WELL,
IT'S TOO LATE FOR SORRY.

29:36.640 --> 29:37.732
DRINK?

29:37.740 --> 29:40.459
ABSOLUT, NEAT.

29:49.580 --> 29:51.810
